43:09.788 --> 43:12.257
- COME TO OFFER
MY CONGRATULATIONS.

43:12.290 --> 43:14.259
- WHY? YOUR TEAM WON.

43:14.292 --> 43:15.827
- NOT BY MUCH.

43:15.861 --> 43:17.328
- [laughs]

43:17.362 --> 43:18.830
- YOU GUYS WERE GREAT.

43:18.864 --> 43:20.999
- OH, THANKS.
- THANKS, CARL.

43:23.769 --> 43:25.771
- HEY, HORVATH?

43:29.775 --> 43:34.780
DOESN'T THE WINNER
BUY THE LOSER A DRINK?

43:34.813 --> 43:36.181
DON'T FLATTER YOURSELF.

43:36.214 --> 43:38.850
NOBODY HERE'S
INTERESTED IN YOU.

43:38.884 --> 43:41.052
EXCEPT ME.

43:47.726 --> 43:49.260
- OH, MY.
OH, OH. OKAY, OKAY.

43:49.294 --> 43:51.797
OH. OH.
- OH.

43:51.830 --> 43:55.166
- [laughs]
- [howling]

43:59.838 --> 44:03.141
- A STRAIGHT KISS AT WOODY'S.

44:03.174 --> 44:05.110
THAT'S GOTTA BE A FIRST.

44:05.143 --> 44:07.045
- I GUESS PEOPLE
REALLY DO FIND LOVE

44:07.078 --> 44:08.747
IN THE STRANGEST PLACES.

44:08.780 --> 44:10.181
WHAT ABOUT YOU, TEDDY?

44:10.215 --> 44:11.850
YOU, UH,
YOU SEE ANYBODY HERE

44:11.883 --> 44:13.952
MAKES YOUR HEART
GO PITTER-PAT?

44:13.985 --> 44:17.789
- WELL, MAYBE.
YEAH? WHO? WHO?

44:17.823 --> 44:19.725
- IT'S TOO SOON TO TELL.

44:19.758 --> 44:22.027
- OH.
- [chuckles]

44:22.060 --> 44:24.763
- I'M GOING TO PRETEND
I DIDN'T JUST SEE MY MOTHER

44:24.796 --> 44:27.165
STICKING HER TONGUE DOWN
HORVATH'S THROAT.

44:27.198 --> 44:28.299
- WHILE YOU'RE AT IT,

44:28.333 --> 44:29.334
PRETEND SHE WON'T
BE BLOWING HIM LATER

44:29.367 --> 44:33.038
IN THE BACK
OF HIS PATROL CAR.

44:35.506 --> 44:39.778
- IT'S TOO BAD JUSTIN
COULDN'T BE HERE TONIGHT.

44:39.811 --> 44:42.147
- I'M OUT OF HERE.

44:42.180 --> 44:44.916
[overlapping chatter]

44:55.026 --> 44:57.763
- SOMEONE ELSE IS WEARING
THE SAME SHIRT AS YOU?

44:57.796 --> 44:59.798
[background chatter
continues]

44:59.831 --> 45:04.435
- YOU TOLD HIM, DIDN'T YOU?
- OH, NO.

45:04.469 --> 45:07.338
- HE DIDN'T SEEM TO CARE.

45:10.976 --> 45:17.115
- [humming]

45:25.957 --> 45:28.927
JESUS, BRIAN.

45:28.960 --> 45:29.995
I THOUGHT YOU WERE BOWLING.

45:30.028 --> 45:31.529
- GAME'S OVER.

45:31.562 --> 45:33.264
- HOW'D WE DO?

45:33.298 --> 45:35.433
- THREE CHEERS
TO THE WINNERS.

45:35.466 --> 45:39.170
- WAY TO GO.

45:39.204 --> 45:40.205
- [sighs]

45:40.238 --> 45:41.907
- IT WASN'T US.

45:41.940 --> 45:45.143
- OH.

45:45.176 --> 45:46.912
- WHERE'RE YOU GOING?

45:46.945 --> 45:48.880
- TAKING A SHOWER.

45:48.914 --> 45:51.482
- YOU SURE ARE TAKING
A LOT OF SHOWERS LATELY.

45:51.516 --> 45:54.552
COME HERE.

45:54.585 --> 45:56.287
- LATER.

45:56.321 --> 45:57.956
- NOW.

45:57.989 --> 46:01.793
- CAN'T WE PLEASE
DO THIS AFTER I SHOWER?

46:01.827 --> 46:05.263
- I LIKE SMELLING YOU.

46:05.296 --> 46:07.265
NOT SOAP.

47:33.084 --> 47:35.020
YOU LIKE THAT?
- YES.

47:44.095 --> 47:48.499
[pants]

47:48.533 --> 47:51.336
WHY'D YOU STOP?

47:53.204 --> 47:56.174
BRIAN?

47:56.207 --> 47:58.343
- [sniffs]

47:58.376 --> 48:00.979
GO TAKE A SHOWER.

48:01.012 --> 48:04.015
YOU STINK.

